reviews.text: The server is not very good attitude when I ask if can change the favor of the icecream , too rigid on changing the ingredients of the dish
With gimick, but the desert is fare

Good presentation of desserts but they don't taste as good as it looks. The waffle are kinda cold and very soft in texture, which I expect to be hotter and crispy. The green tea ice cream is filled with ice pellets and I cannot taste the matcha flavor from that.
Pretty good dessert place.
Nice, waffles were freshly prepared!!
